{
  "id": "L24",
  "title": "Leaving a Voicemail Message",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "In this lesson, you'll learn how to leave a clear and effective voicemail message in Spanish, or 'un mensaje de voz'. This is a very useful skill!"
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V01",
      "data": {
        "El mensaje de voz": "The voicemail message"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Hola",
        "meaning": "Hello"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Por favor, deje su mensaje",
        "meaning": "Please, leave your message"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Soy...",
        "meaning": "I am..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mi dirección es...",
        "meaning": "My address is..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V02",
      "data": {
        "La calle": "The street"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V03",
      "data": {
        "El número": "The number"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mi apellido se deletrea...",
        "meaning": "My last name is spelled..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L24_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "deletrea",
        "phonetic": "de-le-tre-a",
        "tip": "In Spanish, every vowel is pronounced clearly. Practice saying each syllable distinctly: de-le-tre-a."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L24_S01",
      "title": "Starting the Voicemail",
      "setting": "You are calling your housing agency, but you get their voicemail. You need to introduce yourself.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Greet and state your name",
          "chatbot_message": "Hola. Por favor, deje su mensaje. *BEEP*",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_name": "Extract the user's name from their message"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "State your address"
        },
        {
          "title": "Spell your last name"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great start! Now you need to explain the reason for your call. Let's learn how to describe a problem."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Llamo porque...",
        "meaning": "I'm calling because..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V04",
      "data": {
        "La calefacción": "The heating"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "no funciona",
        "meaning": "it doesn't work"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V05",
      "data": {
        "Desde": "Since"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V06",
      "data": {
        "Esta mañana": "This morning"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Hace mucho frío",
        "meaning": "It is very cold"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V07",
      "data": {
        "En la casa": "In the house"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L24_S02",
      "title": "Stating the Problem",
      "setting": "You continue your voicemail message by explaining what the problem is.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "State the reason for your call"
        },
        {
          "title": "Say when the problem started"
        },
        {
          "title": "Explain the consequence"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Excellent. To finish your message, you need to ask them to call you back and provide your number."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Pueden llamarme",
        "meaning": "Can you (plural/formal) call me"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L24_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mi número de teléfono es...",
        "meaning": "My phone number is..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L24_V08",
      "data": {
        "Cero": "Zero"
      }
    },
